Question: Are there helmets or suitcases that are hard?

Reference Answer: yes

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n489699.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='suitcase')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='hard')
ANSWER0=COUNT(box=BOX1)
BOX2=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='helmet')
IMAGE1=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX2)
BOX3=LOC(image=IMAGE1,object='hard')
ANSWER1=COUNT(box=BOX3)
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0} > 0 or {ANSWER1} > 0 else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
